text_help.cn: 点击选择2个不同的色块交换位置, 需要使他们全部回到正确的位置上, 下方的文字会提示当前结果的正确数量。
text_help.en: click to select 2 different color blocks to exchange positions, and you need to make them all return to the correct position. The text below will prompt the correct number of current results.

text_describe.cn: <猜猜乐>是一款简单烧脑的解谜游戏, 玩家需要正确的排列随机出现的色块才能闯关成功, 简单的画风和操作可以让玩家感受到烧脑游戏的乐趣, 快来一起加入挑战吧!
text_describe.en: <Guessers> is a simple brain-burning puzzle game, players need to correctly arrange the random color blocks to pass the success, simple painting style and operation can let the player feel the fun of brain-burning game, come and join the challenge together!
